    "John Trapp": "Behold, I come quickly ] Therefore quicken your pace, bestir yourselves lustily; your time is short, your task is long, your wages inconceivable.\nVer.\n12. This river is Christ, #Joh 4:14, [v_Rev_22_2] and so is that tree of life, #Re 22:\n12. Behold, I come quickly] Therefore quicken your pace, bestir yourselves lustily; your time is short, your task is long, your wages inconceivable.\nVer."
